OL,3,CMan sentenced after "horrific" crash
OL,4,Cwhich seriously injured three people
OL,6,FOne of the passengers suffered a
OL,7,Fshattered pelvis when it became
OL,8,Fdetached from her spine and lost her
OL,9,Fjob due to her injuries. A victim
OL,10,Fimpact statement read to the court
OL,11,Fsaid how, at the age of just 20, she
OL,12,Fhas been told to "expect pain for the
OL,13,Frest of my life."
OL,15,FAnother passenger in the vehicle
OL,16,Frequired spinal surgery and suffered
OL,17,Fbroken ribs, nerve damage and had to
OL,18,Flearn to walk again. She too was
OL,19,Fdismissed from her job due to her
OL,20,Finjuries.
