OL,3,CMan sentenced after "horrific" crash
OL,4,Cwhich seriously injured three people
OL,6,FOne man who was travelling in the car
OL,7,Fsaid he now does not want to go out
OL,8,Ffollowing the crash.
OL,10,FMembers of the public had to
OL,11,Fadminister first aid to the passengers
OL,12,Fat the scene until emergency services
OL,13,Farrived.
OL,15,FFootage shows the moments before and
OL,16,Fafter the crash - including Crocker
OL,17,Frunning from the scene and attempting
OL,18,Fto hide from police. Pictures from
OL,19,FCleveland Police.
