OL,3,CMan sentenced after "horrific" crash
OL,4,Cwhich seriously injured three people
OL,6,FCrocker was detained after he was
OL,7,Ffound hiding nearby. After failing he
OL,8,Ffailed a roadside breath test, he also
OL,9,Frefused to provide a further sample
OL,10,Fand pleaded guilty to three counts of
OL,11,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,12,Fdriving and having no insurance.
OL,14,FIn Court, Crocker was handed 30 months
OL,15,Fin a young offenders institution and a
OL,16,F36-month driving ban.
