OL,3,CMan sentenced after "horrific" crash
OL,4,Cwhich seriously injured three people
OL,6,F"Crocker left the scene to try to
OL,7,Fevade police and avoid the
OL,8,Fconsequences of his actions. He was an
OL,9,Finexperienced driver who was under the
OL,10,Finfluence of alcohol, he had been
OL,11,Fdriving at more than twice the speed
OL,12,Flimit and he was not wearing a
OL,13,Fseatbelt. In a video recording taken
OL,14,Fmoments before the collision, he was
OL,15,Falso clearly distracted. Not one but
OL,16,Fall of the 'fatal four' factors have
OL,17,Fbeen evident in this collision.
