OL,3,CMan sentenced after "horrific" crash
OL,4,Cwhich seriously injured three people
OL,6,F"I welcome the sentence handed to
OL,7,FDylan Crocker and hope it sends a
OL,8,Fstark message to all drivers that
OL,9,Ftaking risks with lives can have
OL,10,Fdevastating consequences. This
OL,11,Fcollision has certainly completely
OL,12,Fchanged not only the lives of the
OL,13,Finjured passengers, but also those of
OL,14,Ftheir families.
